name: MSU CAS117 Space Escape
description: MSU CAS 117 Space Escape by Kaijia Joanna Zhan. This is a 2D platformer that has two modified enemies. One of the enemies is a different shade and has one more health. The other is a boss that has a different sprite and shade and has 10 health in total. Another modification, the arena is bigger in levels 2 and 3.
